Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 晶马…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.25,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}くるくるまわる　君の瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.07,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}探してまわる　駅のホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.16,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}響くファンファーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.36,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ガラガラ音をたてる街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.27,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}とりあえず　耳を貸してみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:23.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　消えるはずの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.15,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:37.98,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もう二度と会えないような　そんな気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.35,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}臨界点を突破してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.51,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}限界ならすでに去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:53.84,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶対的支配だって　崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:59.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}終末理論は机上の　空論でしかないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:10.29,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}0と1の世界線の果てから　叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:18.91,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　君が会いに来るような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:24.44,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕は目を閉じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}转啊转 你的眼睛不停转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.07,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在月台四处寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.16,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}号角声在空中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}大街上轰轰作响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总之 先倾听这声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:23.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在这个就要消逝的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.15,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:37.98,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总是觉得 我们无法再度相会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.35,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命运也在嘲笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}突破临界点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.51,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}极限已然消去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:53.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}就算被绝对地支配 也让它崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:59.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}末日理论无非是一纸空谈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:10.29,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在0与1的世界线的尽头 呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:18.91,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}总是觉得 你即将来与我相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:24.44,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我 就闭上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸没事的样子 睡得像滩烂泥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说笨蛋不会感冒 看来也不会受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样说没关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥… 阳毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小冠一接到医院打来的电话 脸色就变得煞白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴 绝对不要告诉晶马哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要准备早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里是…医院?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你就死在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得昨天发生的事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶被车撞到 就住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有记忆的话 就说明脑袋没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应有点慢那是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有骨折 只是轻微磕碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生也笑着说你运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 虽然小冠嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他从昨天开始就没合过眼 一直陪在小晶的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我去叫苹果过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶要好好向她道谢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是苹果叫的救护车 一直寸步未离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶醒过来了哦 现在很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想向苹果道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我没有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出的事故 还有荻野目苹果的那件东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者是有关联的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…你是被那女人撞出去的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是我又犯傻了呢 还是多管闲事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这纯粹是偶然事故 不是她的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有收到过女孩子送的礼物么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷不丁地说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小冠很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶说你是花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋 又对阳毬说奇怪的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子送你什么样的礼物 你会开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从其他女孩子那里得到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么特别想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的东西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那倒是有很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 会说「这是我倾注心意做成的」那类东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想 比如便当 就有人做得异常精致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切得极其复杂的章鱼小香肠之类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从断面看还是花朵或动物图案的寿司卷之类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 那种挺让人毛骨悚然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 便当不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊 大得出奇的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还放着穿婚纱的情侣娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个确实是来势汹汹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只…只有这些?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 最受不了的还是手织毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还有超级显眼的名字 那个太郁闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在我被迫穿着它的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围巾之类的 你肯定也觉得麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚所说的 全部都是玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢对阳毬手织礼物挑三拣四的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上是不存在的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能收到阳毬送的围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么时候 什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是身处极热的撒哈拉沙漠正中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会把人热瘫的热带雨林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会好好地围给你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手织万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viva 围巾!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}viva，意大利语万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 我会织得让你围得舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回家里一趟 去取小晶的换洗衣物哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 小冠你就去陪陪小晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时发生的事情 你帮我瞒着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:08:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到冠叶和阳毬 真相就说不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖…擦伤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的伤么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用感觉这么愧疚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什么大不了的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院什么的 太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那时候 我也说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过已经没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 日记没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今天我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被撕破了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一半…被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天日记不是掉到马路上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时被一个骑摩托车的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 得赶紧碾碎掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓 该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还特地为你准备了美味甜点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一波未平 一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真讨厌 茶水没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热水室离这里有点远 你认识路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你啊 高仓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友一直陪在身边照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很叫人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 茶水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 艾丝梅拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样引诱猎物上钩的饵就到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始狩猎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不见了 是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是在吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晶马发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.2\frz14.092\fs40\pos(525,405)}把「日记的另一半」交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.2\frz14.092\fs40\pos(400,487)}不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fay0.2\frz14.092\pos(462,520)}高仓晶马就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日记的另一半」?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.16,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA8A8A8&\pos(240,481)}补充：
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.16,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA8A8A8&\pos(358,545)}高仓晶马他，现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,481)}补充：
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,545)}高仓晶马他，现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日记当作交换条件 到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有前半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「被抢走了」 被谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来了一辆摩托车 硬抢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 摇摇晃晃乱走差点被车撞的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被晶马他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不是在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是晶马来救我 现在我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}咦 这里晒的内裤不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个的话 晶马就危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就赶紧…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 不这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.24,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.2\frz339.596\pos(463,527)}高仓冠叶带着「日记」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.24,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.2\frz339.596\pos(403,561)}到C栋的屋顶上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马暂且还平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们也不是全无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎呀哎呀 我的内裤不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}老太太 我们现在就帮您去找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件是从晶马的手机发送过来的 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晶马被关在这医院的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还是你拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只剩一半 这也是阳毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们所需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么 也绝对不能交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不拿去的话晶马他就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会救出晶马的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个就由你来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是你就算要把晶马耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不肯交给他的重要东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照说好的 我把「日记」拿来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我想起什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也想不起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样? 就算这样也不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个穿起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有选择的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给高仓冠叶的指示是个圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻野目苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把日记拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 高仓晶马就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日记从那里扔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 桃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别给我胡搞了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧放了晶马!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于想起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毛衣 很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对你而言 鸽血色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.08,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(741,660)}pigeon blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸽子鲜血的艳红色最适合不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 你的目的是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道日记的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对沿着阿里阿德涅的红线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}古希腊神话中英雄忒修斯，用阿里阿德涅\N给的红线破解了米诺斯的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找到这里的虚伪的勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得表扬一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 那人是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同计划的一样 日记已到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是期待接下来的发展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丝梅拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.97,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(449,275)}请珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.97,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(811,275)}回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 要把「M计划」完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那种会让猎物逃走的愚蠢猎人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 战略!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}10{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:16.11,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}全てがもし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.78,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}決められてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:28.80,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らはどうして　もがくのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:32.96,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}それは、君じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:36.66,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君の、せいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:44.15,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲しみはもうたくさんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:48.00,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}だから、そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.93,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今の、ままじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:59.39,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}うまく伝えきれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:07.17,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:18.37,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
